@node wha "What is the Eye Viewer"

  What is the Eye Viewer?  Eye Viewer  is a program  to explore  your hard
disk in search of graphs and sounds; using the datatypes for every format,
showing the images inside the window of the program and playing the sounds
or songs.

  Beside  exploring  we have  the  options to  manipulate  the  images and
sounds;  we can to copy, to erase,  to move and to rename;  in case of the
images we can  to move inside the own image  when this it exceeds the size
of the  screen of the Eye Viewer,  as the options  to rotate the image; in
case of the sounds we have the Play and Stop's basic options to be able to
playing or to stop the sound or music to that we are listening.
  Also we can to use the Eye Viewer Velazquez as slideshow of our favorite
images, sounds and musics.

  The  Eye Viewer  that  comes in  this  package  is  without  registering
allowing to visualize only 16 images;  once registered you will be able to
enjoy it without restrictions.

  Available in the next languages:
    1. Spanish.
    2. English.
    3. Hrvatski.
    4. Français.
    5. Deutsch.
    6. Italiano.

@endnode

@node requisi "Requesitions"

  This program for make work in your Amiga or UAE, you need them datatypes
for the next formats:
  Graphics: BMP, GIF, IFF, JPG, LBM, PBM, PCX, PGM, PIC, PNG, PNM, PSD,
            PPM, QRT, TGA, TIF.
  Sounds: 8SVX, SVX, MAUD, MOD, WAV.

The libraries:
  mpega for playing mp3-mp2 files
  render v.16
  guigfx v.30
  mathtrans

AHI.
CPU 68020 or highter.
Workwench 3.1 or Amiga O.S. 3.5 and 3.9.
AGA or graphical card.

  Compatible 100% with MorphOS 1.4.5

  Notices: The Eye Viewer not works in Amiga with O.S. 4.0 and Amikit.

@endnode

@node how "How use it?"

  To use  the Eye Viewer it  is necessary  to have  installed in your hard
disk, also you need the code key to be able to use it without restrictions.

  The management of the Eye Viewer  is very easy, we are going to explain,
what do the buttons and the options of the menus.

  Direct access to Eye Viewer.
 @{"  " link accegb} Direct Access.

  Use of short cuts of keyboard and the buttons.
 @{"  " link teclgb} Keyboard @{"  " link botogb} Buttons

  The menus.
 @{"  " link menugb} Menu     @{"  " link opciongb} Options    @{"  " link edicgb} Edition    @{"  " link favogb} Favorites
 @{"  " link zoomgb} Zoom     @{"  " link mirr} Mirror     @{"  " link slidegb} Slideshow  @{"  " link infogb} Information

@endnode

@node ema "E-Mailware?"

  @{b}E-Mailware@{ub}? Yes, the Eye Viewer now is MailWare,  if it is interested to
you;  you send us  one E-Mail  with your name, surnames  and your language
preferential;  spent a few days you will  receive your  personal code key,
with that you  can use  him without  limitations  and of  totally free and
without that  this  supposes that  your mail address  between to forming a
part of mail lists neither the sending of spam for our part.

  The system of key code is to verify the interest that has our program in
Amiga's community and to  continue improving the Eye Viewer, as well as to
continue creating programs and games for Amiga.

@endnode

@node evolu "Evolutions"

Evolutions and improvements of the Eye Viewer:

  @{u}The innovation of the version Velazquez:@{uu}
   - Now when we initiate the E.W. it is  opened according to the size and
     resolution of screen that we have in the Workbench.
   - From an attached icon to a file,  we start the  Eye Viewer that us it
     will show or reproduce it.
   - Rewritten the menus in English, to adapt them to the typical language
     in the programs of this class.
   - Now the Eye Viewer copies, erases, moves and renames files,  with the
     particularity  of that if two  files coincide  with the  same name in
     case of  the graphs is  opened a  window  that shows  them to us, for
     compare them and to be able to change the name of the file that we go
     to copy.
   - It guards  the routes of  destiny where  we have moved  or copied the
     files in a list that we can to change.
   - Improved the option of search of files.
   - Now  we can to select  the size of the mouse pointer and the speed of
     displacement for the screen of the Eye Viewer, when the images exceed
     the size of the same one.
   - Independent or joint searches of sounds, images or MP3 songs.
   - Added the option to do a slideshow with the images inside a directory.
   - Added the option to save the personal configuration of the E.W.
   - Added the option to reproduce music in format mp3.
   - Now we have Play and Stop's buttons, for the sounds or songs.
   - Added favorites' option to accede to our  folders or directories that
     we more use.
   - Corrected  some bugs in the  installer and the  texts of the messages
     now also we have the option to install this guide.

  @{u}The innovation of the version 2.1:@{uu}
   - Added the possibility of using other  datatypes besides them original
     of Amiga O.S.
   - Added the option to choose smoothed only availably in  graphical mode
     of 8 bits.
   - Change the graph and the animation  in the menu "About" for one  only
     standard and definitive animation.

 @{u}The innovation of the version 2.0:@{uu}
  - When setting the pointer on oversize pictures you can also move up and
    down, left and right with a click on the left mouse key.
  - Zoom for increase or dimish one image, with the keys + and -.
  - Search one image for its name.
  - Mirror option we can rotation one image vertical or horizontal.

 @{u}The innovation of the version 1.2:@{uu}
  - Correction of bugs.
  - The installer now  allows to install the new languages without it need
    to have to return to install the program again.

 @{u}The innovation of the version 1.1:@{uu}
  - Now we can  displace with arrows keys up or  down for the names of the
    images and automaticly it is show into  of the left window.
  - With the Enter key you can ajust the image a its real size or to scale.

@endnode

